{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/time-min-milliseconds/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/keyframes-name-pattern/","description":"number-max-precision 限制数字中允许的小数位数 选项 int：允许的最大小数位数。 例如，使用 2： 以下模式被视为违规： 以下模式不被视为违规： 可选的辅助选项 ignoreUnits: \\[\"/regex/\", /regex/, \"string\"]…","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"number-max-precision\"><a href=\"#number-max-precision\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>number-max-precision</h1>\n<p>限制数字中允许的小数位数</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3.245634px</span>; }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**           ↑\n * 这些小数位 */</span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<p><code>int</code>：允许的最大小数位数。</p>\n<p>例如，使用 <code>2</code>：</p>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3.245px</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3.245634px</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> (min-width: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3.234em</span>) {}</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3.24px</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> (min-width: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3.23em</span>) {}</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"可选的辅助选项\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%89%E7%9A%84%E8%BE%85%E5%8A%A9%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>可选的辅助选项</h2>\n<h3 id=\"ignoreunits-regex-regex-string\"><a href=\"#ignoreunits-regex-regex-string\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>ignoreUnits: [\"/regex/\", /regex/, \"string\"]</code></h3>\n<p>忽略具有指定单位的值的数字精度。</p>\n<p>例如，使用 <code>2</code>。</p>\n<p>给定：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-js\">[<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"/^my-/\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"%\"</span>]</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3.245px</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3.245634px</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> (min-width: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3.234em</span>) {}</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3.245%</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> (min-width: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3.23em</span>) {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10.5432%</span>;\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">3.245</span>my-unit; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10.989</span>my-other-unit;\n}</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/number-max-precision.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/number-max-precision/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/number-max-precision/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/number-max-precision/index.html.bcb0eb120759a585710eaf0fb4aa714e.json"}